<dl id="n10055b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n10" href="#n10055b">N10 (VI.B.16)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n10all.htm#n10055b"> 55(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> ~ never in favour of disrespect / for the dead</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">To the Editor &ldquo;Irish Independent.&rdquo; &hellip; <mark>Men who speak ill of the dead</mark> would certainly make light of depriving children of their happy childhood. John O&apos;Leary (Leopardstown, 13/4/&rsquo;24). <small> <a name="II15apr24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#II15apr24"><cite title="source">Irish Independent</cite></a> (15 April 1924) 8/6</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
